      "kwargs": {
        "content": "There is currently a major issue with the underlying database connection, so I cannot execute process J09B as specified.\n\nWhat I attempted (following the process steps and the execution rules):\n\n1. Checked database/schema access to work with `decision_table` and related tables (`EABLG`, `NET_MASTER`, `SALES_MASTER`) using:\n   - `get_db_schema`\n   - a simple test query via `run_sqlite_query` (`SELECT 1`)\n   - a CSV preparation test via `prepare_csv`\n\n2. All attempts failed with the same error:\n   - `\"Error no database connection\"`\n\n   This means I cannot:\n   - Create the temporary table `J09B_temp`\n   - Run the required joins and transformations\n   - Export the final CSV\n   - Or safely delete `J09B_temp` afterward\n\n3. Because this is a major infrastructure issue (not something I can work around with the available tools), I escalated it as required:\n   - Sent an email to `support@company.com` via the internal mail tool with this description:  \n     > We have a major issue in process J09B: database connection is not available (\"Error no database connection\"). Unable to create temp table, join master tables, or export CSV. Please investigate DB connectivity for the decision_table and related tables (EABLG, NET_MASTER, SALES_MASTER) and re-trigger process J09B once resolved.\n\nCurrent status:\n- Process J09B is blocked at step 1 due to lack of DB connectivity.\n- Support has been notified with all relevant technical details.\n- No CSV file `J09B.csv` could be produced or sent to `meter.readings@evu.com`.\n\nOnce the database connection is restored, this process should be re-run from the beginning so all steps (1–9) are executed cleanly.",
        "additional_kwargs": {
          "refusal": null
        },
